book:
  PMB : User Guide


    14 juillet 2006



This guide is the user documentation of PMB, a free and opensource
      integrated library management system, using a PHP/MySQL interface. This
      user documentation is intended for the library staff, and not users of
      the library, that is, the borrowers.


For more information, see www.sigb.net





      2006

      PMB Services SARL and PMB Group of developers




